{"lemma":"صَمَمُ","slug":"صَمَمُ","root":"ص.م.م","root_slug":"ص-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24841","n24847"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deafen (someone)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to resolve, to make up one's mind"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to design, to configure, to devise, to contrive, to fix (something)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deafness","examples":[{"text":"أَنَا الَّذِي نَظَرَ الْأَعْمَى إِلَى أَدَبِي / وَأَسْمَعَتْ كَلِمَاتِي مَنْ بِهِ صَمَمُ","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤam.ma.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24841","headword_ar":"صمّم","root":"Sm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", said of a sword, (S, M, K, TA,) accord. to the K, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It struck the joint, and cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severed, it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tab~aqa","text_ar":"طَبَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but this is at variance with what is said by J and other leading authorities; which is as follows: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it penetrated into the bone, and cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severed, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but when it strikes the joint, and cuts, or severs, it, one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tab~aqa","text_ar":"طَبَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; a poet says, describing a sword,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"yuSam~imu A^aHoyaAnFA waHiynFA yuTab~iqu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It penetrates into the bone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes, and at one time it strikes the joint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it passed into the bones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamoSama","text_ar":"صَمْصَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a sword, signifies the same: (M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSomiymN","text_ar":"تَصْمِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a sword's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penetrating into that which is struck with it without its causing any sound to be heard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~amamu","text_ar":"الصَّمَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the ear. (Ham p. 326.) ―         -b2-  And hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSomiymN","text_ar":"تَصْمِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (tropical:)  A man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping constantly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perseveringly, to the thing that he purposes, until he attains"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ham ubi suprà.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~ama EalaY ka*aA","text_ar":"صَمَّمَ عَلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kept constantly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perseveringly, to his opinion in respect of such a thing, after his desiring to do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm~m","text_ar":"صمّم"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSomiymN","text_ar":"تَصْمِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went on, with penetrative energy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with sharpness, vigorousness, and effectiveness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K, TA,) in an affair, (M, Msb, K, TA,) and in journeying, (S, K, TA,) in this case said of a horse, (Z, TA,) and in other things; (S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamoSama","text_ar":"صَمْصَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bit, and infixed his canine teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not let go what he bit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm~m fiY EaD~atihi","text_ar":"صمّم فِى عَضَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he infixed his teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"canine teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his bite."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm~m","text_ar":"صمّم"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfarasa AlEalafa","text_ar":"الفَرَسَ العَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enabled the horse to take of the fodder to such a degree that fat and repletion stuffed him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm~m","text_ar":"صمّم"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAHibahu AlHadiyva","text_ar":"صَاحِبَهُ الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made his companion to retain the narrative,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story, in his memory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b7-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","TA","Msb","Z"]},{"entry_id":"n24847","headword_ar":"صَمَمٌ","root":"Sm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of the intrans. verb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a","text_ar":"صَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, * M, Msb, K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SimoSimN","text_ar":"صِمْصِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}